<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=3917&amp;p=31059#p31059"><![CDATA[
Additional NMIs only happen when NMIs are being enabled from a disabled state ($2000.7 is going from 0-&gt;1).  If the game enables NMIs when they're already enabled, nothing happens.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=33">Disch</a> — Tue Feb 19, 2008 2:44 pm</p><hr />
